biography: Lasse is a seasoned competitor in the annual Hector Trophée, having participated in each of the previous four tournaments.  Hailing from Tapiola Golf, Lasse brings a wealth of experience to the event.  His consistent appearances speak to his dedication and skill.

While Lasse has yet to claim victory in either the Hector Trophée team competition or the individual Victor trophy, his repeated participation demonstrates his commitment to the tournament and his resilience in the face of challenging competition.  He is undoubtedly a player to watch as the tournament unfolds.
